abstract: Jessica Korda, Stacy Lewis and Azahara Munoz remain tied for first place following first round of the Coates Golf Championship, the LPGA Tour's season opener.
lead_paragraph: Jessica Korda, Stacy Lewis and Azahara Muñoz each shot a six-under-par 66 in the first round of the L.P.G.A. Tour’s season opener, the Coates Golf Championship in Ocala, Fla.
